ARDUINO UNO INFOMARTION

MICROCONTROLLER
     ATmega328P

PIN DETAILS
    The board features 14 digital input/output pins, of which 6 can be used as PWM outputs, and 6 analog input pins for reading analog signals.

COMMUNICATION
       Communication interfaces available on the board include UART (Serial), I2C, and SPI, allowing it to interface with a wide variety of sensors, modules.

USB Interface
       USB Type-B port for programming and power

APPLICATIONS
      Embedded systems, IoT projects, robotics, automation, and prototyping.
